summary: An ordinance accepting an easement from Oscar Systad over a portion of the north 7 feet of the south 357 feet of the SW 1/4 of the SW 1/4 of the NW 1/4 of Section 19, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., for sanitary sewer purposes, and authorizing execution of a statutory quit claim deed in connection therewith.
